Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:23.02,SuperscriptTop,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,251.2)}高二分班表
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:18.30,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,我们在一个班
